data.title: Jennie Cullum Kittrell Fugitt Byars [KBKB 8012MmTNMLObFgqMmBu]7 (1879
data.meta_description: Jennie Cullum Kittrell was born on April 21, 1879 in Pleasant Shade, Smith County, Tennessee, daughter of John Bell Kittrell and Julia Elizabeth Ballou. She was married on June 10, 1910 in Woodbury, Cannon County, Tennessee to Talmon Fugitt, they gave birth to 1 child. She was married on December  9, 1914 in Dibrell,Warren County, Tennessee to Perry Green Byars. She died on June 23, 1961 in McMinnville, Warren County, Tennessee. This information is part of Genealogy Kittrell by Wm. Samuel McAliley II aided by foundation built by Henny Carlisle in 2003 on Genealogy Online.
